beat-up hot rod truck,

01:22.340 --> 01:24.080
which would have
a fresh, new frame.

01:24.080 --> 01:26.310
A nice looking engine,
a rebuilt suspension,

01:26.320 --> 01:27.780
and really that's what
we're doing to it.

01:27.780 --> 01:29.220
It was a back-burner job for me,

01:29.220 --> 01:31.520
until richard came by my shop.

01:31.520 --> 01:33.750
This is a '33 ford
pickup, and actually--

01:33.760 --> 01:35.220
that's where richard
fell pretty hard

01:35.220 --> 01:36.690
for this '33 ford model b.

01:36.690 --> 01:38.360
No kiddin'.
I bought it for myself,

01:38.360 --> 01:39.560
