02:48.860 --> 02:49.900
What's the deal with the bed?

02:49.900 --> 02:51.270
'cause I saw it has a rip in it.

02:51.270 --> 02:53.830
Yeah, the bed floor
is kinda trashed.

02:53.840 --> 02:55.800
