I realized we had a problem.

03:31.040 --> 03:33.240
Uh, wait, this
isn't gonna bolt in to

03:33.240 --> 03:34.680
our truck the way it is.

03:34.680 --> 03:36.240
No, that is not gonna fit
without

03:36.250 --> 03:38.580
