That sucks.

03:38.580 --> 03:40.380
All we're trying to do is
get it on the engine stand.

03:40.380 --> 03:42.250
That will work in
our truck, but,

03:42.250 --> 03:43.350
to make it work in
our truck we have to

03:43.350 --> 03:44.790
