the front of the engine.

03:44.790 --> 03:46.450
Water pumps, timing
cover, distributor.

03:46.460 --> 03:48.690
All that stuff's in the way.

03:48.690 --> 03:51.230
There's not enough room
to clear the radiator.

03:51.230 --> 03:52.660
We're gonna change all
that to make it fit,

03:52.660 --> 03:54.160
